description: For practical functional commercial outdoor spaces, we have included a range of outdoor furniture extras including parasols and umbrellas ideal for terraces, pubs, pools, spas and cafes.  Our garden parasols are shower-proof and UV resistant and we supply concrete bases and wheeled options for easy movement. We are able to source a wide range of commercial outdoor furniture options, so if you don't see exactly what you are looking for, please call our sales team.
